Determine the output of the following code:

```java
public class Helper
{
    public static int twice(int n)
    {
        return n * 2;
    }

    public static double mix(int a, int b)
    {
        return Math.pow(a, 2) + twice(b);
    }

    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        int x = 3;
        int y = 4;
        System.out.print(mix(x, y));
    }
}
```

